TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard anything about strange animals in the area?
Text: 이 지역에 이상한 동물들에 대한 얘기 들은 적 있어?

TextEng: Can you tell me what's going on in this area?
Text: 이 지역에서 무슨 일이 벌어지는지 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague? Anything?
You hear 'bout weird animals around here?
What go on around here?
Do you know anything else about it?
You knows something else maybe?
Maybe you've heard of something of interest?
I'd be interested in work, if you know of anything.
Are there any places of interest in the core I should visit?
Text: 중심부에 방문할 만한 흥미로운 장소가 있어?

TextEng: Maybe you hears something interesting?
Me want work.
You know good places to go here?
Text: 여기서 갈 만한 좋은 곳 알아?

TextEng: So you haven't heard about any animals in this area?
Text: 그럼 이 지역의 동물들에 대해 들은 게 없다는 거야?

TextEng: So you not hear about animals 'round here?
Text: 그럼 여기 동물 얘기 못 들었어?

TextEng: I'm investigating the plague. Perhaps you could tell me more about it.
Text: 역병을 조사하고 있어. 더 자세히 말해줄 수 있을까?

TextEng: Me look into plague. Maybe you know more?
Text: 나 역병 알아보는 중. 더 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
Can I ask you some directions?
Neverwinter big place. Me need directions.
Text: 네버윈터 큰 곳이야. 길 안내가 필요해.

TextEng: Aren't you in danger of becoming infected yourself?
Text: 네 자신도 감염될 위험이 있는 거 아냐?

TextEng: Where are all these dead people coming from?
Text: 이 모든 시신들은 어디서 오는 거야?

TextEng: This can't be a pleasant task for you.
You not in danger of catching plague here?
Text: 여기 있으면 너도 역병 옮는 거 아냐?

TextEng: Where the dead come from?
This not a nice job, huh?
You believe you'll see your family again when you die?
Text: 죽으면 가족을 다시 만날 거라고 믿어?

TextEng: You're a fool to take such a risk.
Text: 그런 위험을 감수하다니 바보 같은 짓이야.

TextEng: I hope you're right. That you'll see your family.
Text: 네가 맞길 바라지. 가족을 만날 수 있길.

TextEng: May the gods watch over you, brother. May they watch over us all.
Text: 신들이 당신을 지켜주시길, 형제여. 우리 모두를 지켜주시길.

TextEng: You thinks you see family again when you dies?
Text: 너 죽으면 가족 다시 본다 믿어?

TextEng: You'se a fool to think that.
Me hope you'se right, that you sees family again.
Text: 네 말 맞길 바라, 가족 다시 보길.

TextEng: May gods watch over you, brother. May gods watch us all.
Text: 신들 너 지켜주시길, 형제여. 신들 우리 모두 지켜주시길.

TextEng: Uh-huh. Let me ask you something else.
Uhhh... me ask you other question now.
Let me ask you something else, then.
Me have other question.
